dotnet new maui -n BEROS.Mobile
cd BEROS.Mobile

dotnet add package SkiaSharp.Views.Maui.Controls      # 2D Graphics/Canvas
dotnet add package SkiaSharp.Views.Maui                # Particles/Sprites
dotnet add package Microsoft.AspNetCore.SignalR.Client # Multiplayer
dotnet add package CommunityToolkit.Mvvm               # MVVM (optional)

For 3D/Racing: dotnet add package Raylib-CsLo (OpenGL, tractors/particles).
Private Server: Separate console app (dotnet new console -n BEROS.Server):textdotnet add package Microsoft.AspNetCore.SignalR
dotnet run --urls=http://0.0.0.0:5000  # Host on PC (port forward 5000)Friends join via IP:5000/roomcode.

COMPLETE BEROS CODE (Copy-Paste Ready)
